~ hope
Sarah: ...
Sarah: Oh, I really hope he didn't go drinking. 
- He doesn't beat you, does he? => beat
- Why's he not supposed to drink?
	Sarah: He's had some serious problems with it in the past. 
	Sarah: He'd get so drunk sometimes he couldn't find his way home at night. Used to find him in some ditch in the morning, passed out. 
