	Sarah: My dad's birthday is coming up in a few days. Micah's helping me get him a surprise gift. 
	Sarah: It's gonna be really cool. But I can't tell you what it is yet. I don't trust you quite enough.
	Sarah: But since you're Gifted and all, you might help cleanse it right before we give it to him. Have the Goddess bless it through you!
	Sarah: What do you say?
